Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:33.88,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}心頭奔湧難息 與人相生相變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:39.51,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}寒氣襲人 指尖難捨難分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:45.43,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}光暗兩重天 皆可獨善其身
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.14,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}惶恐無益
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.06,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}不期之晨 已不復歸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:53.98,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所重複者 僅為鮮活明艷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:56.98,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}汝亦從此 於世再無瓜葛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.49,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}黃粱短夢堆重疊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.49,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}昔日轟華化永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.25,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}唯留謊言難釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.17,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}予此絕世以痛傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.92,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}心若所願則易惘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.96,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}故而切勿遠離吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:22.55,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}令汝所見之明日 吐息煥然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.47,nopc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}張開雙臂歡笑相迎
